metadata.name: Confusion
metadata.description:
Confusion 
Investigating existential anxieties, emotions, issues, and innermost drives has always intrigued me. I love to give voice to the unspoken, to express the criticality of life and explore states of mind. "Confusion" is my first digital work, from the "Emotions" series, a collage of different images made with the help of artificial intelligence, reworked and animated with my steampunk_psychedelic style.
(Audio on)
